para_trans: Mauje Kohli, Ta. Sadak Arjuni G. Gondia
Here's about approving a new sub-centre.
Government Decision No: Sub-Collector-2024 / P.No.240 / Health-3
10th Floor, Gokuldas Tejpal Hospital Complex Building,
Read: Letter from Health Services Commissionerate, Mumbai No. Asasay / Room-7A / T-5 / Kohlitola / Substation / Establishment / Gondia / 3199-3201/2024, D. 21/08/2024.
Introduction - Mouje Kohlitola, Ta. A proposal to sanction a new sub-station at Sadak Arjuni G. Gondia was under consideration of the Government.

Government Decision - Mouze Kohli Tola, Ta. The sanction of a new sub-station at Sadak Arjuni Gondia is being approved under this Government Decision as a "special matter." in the prescribed manner for this Sub-Centre.
On the acquisition of land and creation of posts after completion of construction by the Zilla Parishad.
This Government decision is available on the website of the Government of Maharashtra www.maharashtra.gov.in.
